        dc:contributor      "Edited: Jassal, B, 2008-05-28 09:06:10" , "GOC:reactome_curators" , "Reviewed: D'Eustachio, P, 2008-05-28 08:30:54" , "Authored: Jassal, Bijay, 2008-10-01" ;
